Package nl.utwente.jmlplugin.annotator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorMessages
    Class that holds all the error messages that can be displayed to the user by the plugin
    ExtraVariables
    Holder for all the variables that are manually kept track of during type checking
    InnerJavaExprResult
    Holds the results of type checking an InnerJavaExpr
    JMLAnnotator
    Does some general checking of the generated PSI Tree
    JMLAnnotatorUtil
    Util class for the annotators containing lookup functions for JML comments
    JMLJavaExprVisitor
    Visits Java PsiExpressions and checks for type errors
    JMLSemanticsAnnotator
    Checks the tree for semantic errors
    JMLSyntaxAnnotator
    Checks the tree for syntax errors
    JMLTypeAnnotator
    Checks the tree for type errors
    JMLTypeAnnotatorUtil
    Util class for JMLTypeAnnotator, deals with java expressions in text from and extra variables
    RangeManager
    Keeps track of changes in text ranges for all elements in an expression
    RangeManager.RangeChange
    Holds a single range change
  • Enum Summary

    CommentPosition
    Enum to keep track of where a JMLComment is placed in the Java file
